This is the INSTALL file for odf-xslt

Copyright (C) 2007 Tribal Internet Marketing BV
Written by Sander Marechal <sander.marechal@tribal.nl>

REQUIREMENTS:

* PHP 5
* XML module for PHP5
* XSL module for PHP5
* PHP CLI (for the commandline tool)

odf-xslt comes with a simple makefile that only understands the install,
uninstall, dist and clean targets. By default, odf-xslt will install in
/usr/local/share/php and it's documentation in /usr/local/share/doc
